<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>Mushrooms</title>
	</head>
	<body>	
    <MainLayout>
      <img src="/mushrooms/banner.png" alt="">
      <div class="flex flex-col px-[12rem] py-10 gap-8">
        <div class="font-semibold text-xl text-center">CORDYCEPS MILITARIS MUSHROOM</div>
        <img src="/mushrooms/branding.png" alt="" class="w-[650px] self-center">
        <div class="text-sm flex flex-col gap-1 w-[500px] text-center self-center">
          <div>
            Cordyceps Militaris is a high profile mushroom which is seldom found in Himalayan mountain ranges and has tremendous medicinal value. It has been used in traditional medicine practices for years in these regions.
          </div>
          <div>
            NIMS The Organic Hub, is the Marketing Partner of this endeavour and is into retail sales of Organic Farming products, while also supporting various Organic Farming Initiatives. Vana Shrubs is itnto Research, Development, Production, Cultivation and Marketing of various mushrooms, with particular focus on "Cordyceps Militaris" mushroom, its by-products, and similarly other mushrooms of significance and their by-products.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="gap-[1px] flex flex-col px-16">
